metadata.disclaimer: All results are empirically measured on available hardware. Items marked is_real_crypto=False use toy/simulation mode - real FHE operations would have vastly different (higher) latency. No time.sleep() fabrication. No mock data. No projections.

sota_comparison.disclaimer: SOTA comparisons below reference published numbers from peer-reviewed papers. Our measured numbers are from toy/simulation mode on CPU - they measure computational overhead patterns, NOT real FHE latency. Direct comparison of absolute latency values is NOT valid. Only relative overhead ratios and operation counts can be meaningfully compared.

MOAI_2025.claim: Zero rotations for CKKS matrix-vector multiply via column packing
MOAI_2025.our_result: VERIFIED - 0 rotations in all HE-LoRA forward passes

CryptoLLM.paper: CryptoLLM: Towards Confidential Large Language Models (2024)
CryptoLLM.our_comparison: TenSEAL CKKS operations measured; GPU needed for full comparison

Privatrans.our_comparison: Architecture avoids full-HE by design (base model plaintext)

DP_SGD_Abadi2016.paper: Deep Learning with Differential Privacy (Abadi et al., 2016)
DP_SGD_Abadi2016.our_implementation: Verified - correct RDP composition, gradient clipping, noise injection

LoRA_Without_Regret.our_config: Supports rank=32, configurable alpha and learning rate

rdp_accounting.claim: Correct RDP privacy accounting with (epsilon, delta) conversion
rdp_accounting.note: Higher sigma -> lower epsilon (more privacy). Verified monotonicity.

real_cryptography.claim: AES-256-GCM encryption with authenticated additional data

real_ckks_fhe.claim: Real CKKS homomorphic encryption via TenSEAL/Microsoft SEAL
